### Why is this important
When proposing a business idea to the senior management and stakeholder, you should always add some facts and figures showing the comparison of some metric **before and after implementation of the idea**. This usually catches the interest of the viewer/listener as he/she might not have in-depth knowledge of the technology behind the idea. All they care is about how the idea can benefit the organization as compared to the current technology being used. So, adding some survey results or figurative comparison we immediately draw their attention.



