> ### *What is done correctly âœ…*
* *The `Robo-Agent` business idea is very clear and focused which makes it very easy to understand  âœ…*
* *Great work mentioning the advantages/benefits of using the `Customer segmentation` technique  âœ…*


> ##### *What is missing âŒ*
* As mentioned in above specification, you need to **keep atleast 2-5 paragraphs for Project Description section too** :x:
* When presenting a solution to the problem , you need to ensure that the solution is :

### Quantifiable 
This part of the solution discusses about **where the solution could be implemented** ie. to which project domains is the solution applicable. So, you need to tell - which all project domains could use the idea of customer segmentation

### Measurable
You need to provide some kind of **metric to measure the effectiveness of the solution.**This is an important part because without some kind of metric, no new solution is implemented in an organization. The metric could be anything such as time, money, resource etc. Please include some metric to your solution, which can be compared before and after implementing the solution.

### Replicable
As the name suggests, the solution should be easily replicable. **You can provide some kind of model / implementation diagram / architecture diagram to show you solution which can be later replicated in the organization. ** For example, a business idea of using Machine Learning in an organization can be overviewed as  :point_down:

![Arch Diag.jpeg](https://udacity-reviews-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/_attachments/263256/1629570108/Arch_Diag.jpeg)

