### Great work adding the some  benefits and ROI for the idea. However, the ROI needs to be something which is quantifiable. For example, time, money etc. As of now, I can find any such ROI in your project model :point_down:
 


### Why this is Important ?
As per personal point of view, the project implementation ideas and benefits looks great. However think from an organization point of view, if you present this idea to senior management or director, the first thing they would look at is the **Profit - be it in terms of time or in terms of money**. So, it becomes most important to include the quantifiable information in order to get attention of higher management.
Try to update this section and  some measurable ROI. 
